IMAPAccount goat
Host imap.gmail.com
User adam.trimble@goat.com
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -s 'imap.gmail.com' -a 'adam.trimble@goat.com' -w"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore goat-remote
Account goat

MaildirStore goat-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/adam.trimble-goat.com/
Inbox ~/.mail/adam.trimble-goat.com/Inbox

Channel goat
Master :goat-remote:
Slave :goat-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
